_TOOL_NAME_
-----------

This tool is just an easy way of creating application skin package.

This tool assumes that its invoked in the "skintools" root directory.
Some assumptions were made as to make this tool as easy to use as possible.
For detailed information head to the scripts and read the comments.

It is required to run '_TOOL_NAME_ -p' before making any modifications to files inside.
If any files are changed before using prepare mod, then _TOOL_NAME_ will refuse to work

Invocation:

  _TOOL_NAME_ -p
    Creates copy of 'skindata_orig' directory to make skin package.

  _TOOL_NAME_ [OPTIONS] <skin_name>
    Creates new skin package.
    OPTIONS:
        -f   Creates full skin package instead of differential
        -s   Manually set app version
